XIU JIAN SUN, Petitioner,
v.
Donald J. TRUMP, President of the United States, et al. No. 19-804 Supreme Court of the United States. Feb. 24, 2020 Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit denied. Justice Kavanaugh took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
